## Event Contracts

### Emitted Events

#### `{{ project_slug }}.status.changed`
**Purpose**: Component status updates
**Payload**:
```json
{
  "component": "{{ project_slug }}",
  "status": "ready|busy|error|offline",
  "timestamp": "ISO8601",
  "metadata": {}
}
```

#### `{{ project_slug }}.error.occurred`
**Purpose**: Error notifications
**Payload**:
```json
{
  "component": "{{ project_slug }}",
  "error_type": "string",
  "message": "string",
  "timestamp": "ISO8601",
  "context": {}
}
```

{# Add project-type specific events #}
